  <refentry xml:id="function.mysql-get-client-info" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>mysql_get_client_info</refname>
    <refpurpose>Aflare informatii client MySQL</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>Descriere</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>string</type><methodname>mysql_get_client_info</methodname>
      <void/>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     <function>mysql_get_client_info</function> intoarce un sir de caractere care 
	 reprezinta versiunea librariei client.
    </para>
    <para>
     <example>
      <title>exemplu <function>mysql_get_client_info</function></title>
      <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
printf("Informatie client MySQL: %s\n", mysql_get_client_info());
?>
]]>
      </programlisting>
      <para>
       Exemplul de mai sus va produce:
      </para>
      <screen>
<![CDATA[
Informatie client MySQL: 3.23.39
]]>
      </screen>
     </example>
    </para>
    <para>
     Va recomandam de asemenea:
     <function>mysql_get_host_info</function>,
     <function>mysql_get_proto_info</function> si
     <function>mysql_get_server_info</function>.
    </para>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

